Ensure your system is using a YUM repository for base packages as well as application streams
FInd the packag that contains the sepolicy program file and install it
Install the previous version of PHP
Downlaod the httpd package from the repositories without instlalling it, and query to see if there are any scripts in it
Answer: yum install yum-plugin-downloadonly; yum install --downloadonly --downloaddir=/tmp httpd
Alternative Answer: yum install yum-utils; yumdownloader httpd
